WEBVTT

1
00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:47.290 
不
No.

2
00:14:47.290 --> 00:14:49.220 
桑迪  他怎么敢笑你
Sandy. How dare he laugh at you.

3
00:14:49.220 --> 00:14:50.920 
他以为他是谁
Who does he think...

4
00:14:50.930 --> 00:14:52.290 
抱歉  我是说"谁"
Sorry. "Who."

5
00:14:53.160 --> 00:14:54.830 
总之呢
Anyway.

6
00:14:54.830 --> 00:14:56.430 
我在你的通讯录里查到了他的住址
I looked up his address in your contact list.

7
00:14:56.430 --> 00:14:58.400 
天啊  你不是真去了吧
Oh, God. Tell me you didn't go over there.

8
00:14:58.400 --> 00:15:01.130 
我严重认为他亟需些"动之以情"
I just thought he needed to listen to common sense

9
00:15:01.140 --> 00:15:02.640 
和"晓之以理"
and reasonable discourse.

10
00:15:02.640 --> 00:15:05.110 
天啊  别说这是给你拳头取的名字吧
Oh, God. Tell me those aren't the names of your fists.

11
00:15:05.110 --> 00:15:06.810 
是哥腿儿的名字
They're my feet.

12
00:15:06.810 --> 00:15:08.140 
哥更擅长踢腿踹人
I'm actually more of a kicker.

13
00:15:08.940 --> 00:15:11.180 
于是乎  我去了他家
So I went to his apartment.

